reviewText: The cover of this looks like another tale of gothic horror from Brain Damage Films. But, Gorno is much more like a Harmony Korrine white trash,kinda like KIDs meets Freaks and Geeks? serial killer tale,, really good punk music,,,Really good acting from the main young kid. Hey they left it wide open to,, Gorno 2 ? I'd buy it!!
I ordered Gorno online and I had my doubts about this being a brand new movie. But I recieved it in brand new condition and on time too. Thanks!
GORNO is just a great low budget film. Quite original, kinda like "Kids meets Halloween".  also has a great soundtrack
